1
00:00:00,461 --> 00:00:08,561
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,736 --> 00:00:16,973
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,211 --> 00:00:19,202
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,216 --> 00:00:25,982
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,053 --> 00:00:29,420
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,623 --> 00:00:33,184
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,561 --> 00:00:36,928
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,998 --> 00:00:44,427
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,505 --> 00:00:53,641
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,714 --> 00:01:01,746
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,989 --> 00:01:08,827
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,896 --> 00:01:16,962
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,271 --> 00:01:25,736
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,813 --> 00:01:27,838
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:47,078 --> 00:01:49,410
The rules are the same as
in the preliminaries.

16
00:01:50,348 --> 00:01:53,977
The match goes on until one of you
dies or admits defeat.

17
00:01:55,353 --> 00:01:57,583
When it's determined that
there's a winner,

18
00:01:57,656 --> 00:01:59,624
the match can be stopped.

19
00:02:00,492 --> 00:02:02,050
But that's my decision.

20
00:02:09,834 --> 00:02:15,238
<i>Bushy Brow's Jutsu. Sasuke Style!</i>

21
00:02:26,017 --> 00:02:28,383
Hey Guy! You too, Lee...

22
00:02:29,354 --> 00:02:30,981
Is your body all right?

23
00:02:31,957 --> 00:02:32,753
Kakashi!

24
00:02:33,325 --> 00:02:34,223
Kakashi Sensei!

25
00:02:37,796 --> 00:02:40,026
Oh! Sorry, sorry.

26
00:02:40,565 --> 00:02:45,002
You must've been worried.
Sorry for not contacting you at all...

27
00:02:47,572 --> 00:02:50,541
<i>Oh no, Sakura's gonna get really mad...</i>

28
00:02:54,646 --> 00:02:57,080
I don't really mind that.

29
00:03:14,899 --> 00:03:17,367
<i>It's hard to see from here...</i>

30
00:03:19,437 --> 00:03:20,426
<i>Sasuke...</i>

31
00:03:24,776 --> 00:03:25,674
Kakashi Sensei...

32
00:03:26,878 --> 00:03:27,401
Hm?

33
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:32,516
You know about the mark
on Sasuke's neck, don't you?

34
00:03:35,687 --> 00:03:36,551
Is that...?

35
00:03:40,125 --> 00:03:41,387
No need to worry.

36
00:03:44,362 --> 00:03:45,124
<i>A mark?</i>

37
00:03:52,871 --> 00:03:54,896
So, that's that.

38
00:03:56,608 --> 00:03:57,131
Yup!

39
00:04:06,151 --> 00:04:06,879
One...

40
00:04:07,752 --> 00:04:08,582
Two...

41
00:04:09,254 --> 00:04:10,084
Three...

42
00:04:10,655 --> 00:04:11,451
Four...

43
00:04:12,891 --> 00:04:13,516
Five...

44
00:04:14,993 --> 00:04:15,721
Six...

45
00:04:16,594 --> 00:04:17,424
Seven...

46
00:04:18,229 --> 00:04:18,991
Eight.

47
00:04:19,698 --> 00:04:20,596
Eight of them...

48
00:04:21,866 --> 00:04:24,130
There are eight members of
Anbu Black Ops in this spacious arena...

49
00:04:24,736 --> 00:04:26,260
Two platoons are too few...

50
00:04:27,872 --> 00:04:29,464
What's Lord Hokage thinking?

51
00:04:30,475 --> 00:04:33,967
Well... without knowing how or when
the opponent would make their move...

52
00:04:34,446 --> 00:04:37,574
It can't be helped that the Anbu
are dispersed and deployed

53
00:04:37,682 --> 00:04:39,650
in important areas in the village.

54
00:04:40,285 --> 00:04:41,013
Huh?

55
00:04:41,553 --> 00:04:42,315
It's about to begin.

56
00:04:43,221 --> 00:04:45,314
We shouldn't let our guard down,
but for now...

57
00:04:45,757 --> 00:04:48,817
We need to pay attention...
to this match.

58
00:04:52,864 --> 00:04:58,666
Kakashi, I'll be carefully checking out
what sort of training you gave him...

59
00:04:59,804 --> 00:05:01,738
as your eternal rival!

60
00:05:04,676 --> 00:05:06,576
Huh? Did you say something

61
00:05:08,713 --> 00:05:12,274
No! You're slick, Kakashi!

62
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:15,319
Why are you always so avant garde?!

63
00:05:24,529 --> 00:05:26,190
Both of you, to the middle!

64
00:06:27,058 --> 00:06:27,717
Begin!

65
00:06:39,103 --> 00:06:41,970
<i>So this is the sand</i>
<i>Kakashi told me about...</i>

66
00:06:49,247 --> 00:06:52,114
Please don't get so mad...

67
00:06:57,555 --> 00:06:58,852
Mother...

68
00:07:01,226 --> 00:07:03,660
<i>What's he talking about...?</i>

69
00:07:05,296 --> 00:07:10,893
Earlier... Earlier I had you suck
awful tasting blood.

70
00:07:12,237 --> 00:07:13,534
I'm sorry.

71
00:07:15,173 --> 00:07:19,109
But this time it'll likely...

72
00:07:19,944 --> 00:07:21,377
taste good.

73
00:07:23,882 --> 00:07:28,046
His conversation's started.
This is dangerous.

74
00:07:28,586 --> 00:07:32,545
This is the first time I've seen Gaara
get like that before fighting.

75
00:07:33,525 --> 00:07:35,857
So it must mean his opponent
is that imposing...

76
00:07:36,728 --> 00:07:37,251
Him.

77
00:07:47,005 --> 00:07:49,303
It appears he's calmed down.

78
00:07:56,814 --> 00:07:57,610
Come on.

79
00:08:07,158 --> 00:08:07,886
Hey...

80
00:08:11,062 --> 00:08:15,055
Do you remember...
what he said yesterday?

81
00:08:18,836 --> 00:08:20,861
At that time...

82
00:08:31,616 --> 00:08:34,983
<i>I will kill...you all without fail.</i>

83
00:08:36,321 --> 00:08:37,413
<i>Just wait.</i>

84
00:08:38,489 --> 00:08:39,615
That's what he said...

85
00:08:41,893 --> 00:08:43,383
But he didn't do it.

86
00:08:45,296 --> 00:08:47,594
It was the perfect opportunity, but...

87
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:52,533
he didn't even see us.

88
00:08:57,875 --> 00:09:00,366
<i>Now, let me feel it!</i>

89
00:09:02,146 --> 00:09:03,272
We're...

90
00:09:04,649 --> 00:09:06,173
unsatisfactory for him.

91
00:09:07,318 --> 00:09:10,810
Right now, the only one who
can make him feel anything...

92
00:09:11,656 --> 00:09:13,248
...is only Sasuke!

93
00:09:15,593 --> 00:09:19,427
<i>I live fighting for only myself</i>
<i>and loving myself...</i>

94
00:09:20,031 --> 00:09:23,125
<i>And if I see that all other people</i>
<i>in this world</i>

95
00:09:23,201 --> 00:09:25,169
<i>exist only to make me realize that,</i>

96
00:09:26,471 --> 00:09:29,201
<i>there could be no world more wonderful.</i>

97
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:33,842
<i>Naruto...</i>

98
00:09:55,166 --> 00:09:55,894
Here we go

99
00:10:04,776 --> 00:10:07,438
The Sand Shield became
a Sand Clone!

100
00:10:39,644 --> 00:10:41,839
<i>He's fast! This guy...</i>
<i>is just like that guy...</i>

101
00:11:11,175 --> 00:11:15,305
<i>He's fast! It's nearly the same</i>
<i>as Lee's ordinary speed.</i>

102
00:11:15,913 --> 00:11:16,538
<i>And...</i>

103
00:11:17,448 --> 00:11:19,245
<i>It's overlapping with the image...</i>

104
00:11:20,785 --> 00:11:21,774
<i>of my Taijutsu!</i>

105
00:11:26,524 --> 00:11:28,151
Is that the Sand Armor?

106
00:11:32,463 --> 00:11:33,157
Come on!

107
00:11:44,675 --> 00:11:46,734
Thank you, Anbu man.

108
00:11:48,045 --> 00:11:51,981
So apparently, Hinata will be
all right for now if she rests.

109
00:11:53,818 --> 00:11:55,285
Oh, is that right?

110
00:11:59,557 --> 00:12:03,186
Huh? You know this person?
What're you taking about?

111
00:12:03,394 --> 00:12:05,021
This person is an Anbu...

112
00:12:08,466 --> 00:12:12,596
Not that, but at the examination...?
What do you mean?

113
00:12:19,210 --> 00:12:21,576
Well, this is what it means...

114
00:12:54,079 --> 00:12:54,773
Come on!

115
00:13:01,186 --> 00:13:03,313
If you're not gonna come at me,
I'll go at you!

116
00:13:09,528 --> 00:13:10,358
He's fast!

117
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,707
What's the matter? Is that it?

118
00:13:31,083 --> 00:13:32,573
<i>A-Amazing...</i>

119
00:13:37,189 --> 00:13:39,953
That armor... I'll tear it off.

120
00:13:50,302 --> 00:13:54,261
<i>His speed is basically the same</i>
<i>as Lee's with the weights removed.</i>

121
00:13:55,674 --> 00:13:58,905
<i>It's... It's exactly like</i>
<i>Lee's Taijutsu.</i>

122
00:13:59,311 --> 00:14:01,506
<i>His speed is also completely</i>
<i>different from before!</i>

123
00:14:12,257 --> 00:14:16,591
<i>Sasuke... You are indeed</i>
<i>a genius beyond imagination.</i>

124
00:14:17,429 --> 00:14:22,230
<i>How many years did it take me</i>
<i>to attain that speed...?</i>

125
00:14:23,068 --> 00:14:26,663
<i>And you attained it in a mere month...!</i>

126
00:14:38,417 --> 00:14:41,545
<i>However, it seems to consume</i>
<i>a lot of stamina</i>

127
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,815
<i>to continue that movement.</i>

128
00:14:46,458 --> 00:14:48,255
<i>What's Gaara planning to do?</i>

129
00:14:49,261 --> 00:14:51,354
<i>The sand armor uses up too</i>
<i>much Chakra...</i>

130
00:14:52,130 --> 00:14:54,189
<i>It can't last for very long.</i>

131
00:15:04,877 --> 00:15:07,175
What the heck sort of training
did you do?!

132
00:15:07,579 --> 00:15:08,136
Hm?

133
00:15:08,881 --> 00:15:11,577
To get to that level in a mere month...

134
00:15:13,018 --> 00:15:16,545
Sasuke had copied Lee's Taijutsu
with Sharingan.

135
00:15:17,522 --> 00:15:20,252
So during the Taijutsu training...

136
00:15:20,726 --> 00:15:23,388
I had Sasuke image Lee's movements.

137
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:31,430
Sasuke could make
that movement his own

138
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:33,538
only because he knew Lee.

139
00:15:34,606 --> 00:15:37,507
Of course, Sasuke had to
work very hard for it.

140
00:15:38,877 --> 00:15:41,539
<i>But...with only that...</i>

141
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:45,707
<i>With only Taijutsu...</i>
<i>that Sand guy can't be taken down!</i>

142
00:15:49,388 --> 00:15:50,685
<i>That Kakashi...</i>

143
00:15:51,123 --> 00:15:52,818
<i>He must have seen the battle</i>

144
00:15:53,125 --> 00:15:55,685
<i>between the hateful Gaara</i>
<i>and the lovable Lee.</i>

145
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:04,500
<i>Taijutsu that was taught suddenly</i>

146
00:16:04,569 --> 00:16:07,663
<i>can't work against an opponent</i>
<i>that even Lee couldn't take down.</i>

147
00:16:08,273 --> 00:16:09,831
<i>He should have known this only too well.</i>

148
00:16:11,243 --> 00:16:12,335
<i>So if that's the case...</i>

149
00:16:13,412 --> 00:16:16,939
<i>Why is it that he had Sasuke</i>
<i>master only Taijutsu?!</i>

150
00:16:49,348 --> 00:16:53,182
<i>Why did I keep living?</i>

151
00:16:55,687 --> 00:16:59,020
<i>But as long as you're alive,</i>
<i>you need a reason...</i>

152
00:16:59,491 --> 00:17:02,085
<i>If you don't have one,</i>
<i>it's just the same as being dead.</i>

153
00:17:03,261 --> 00:17:05,126
<i>What's this guy saying?!</i>

154
00:17:09,501 --> 00:17:11,901
<i>So this is the answer I came to...</i>

155
00:17:12,504 --> 00:17:16,497
<i>I am living in order to kill</i>
<i>human beings other than myself.</i>

156
00:17:16,975 --> 00:17:20,502
<i>After living in the fear of never knowing</i>
<i>when I might be murdered,</i>

157
00:17:20,712 --> 00:17:22,543
<i>finally, I became calm.</i>

158
00:17:25,751 --> 00:17:26,342
Oh?

159
00:17:27,185 --> 00:17:28,083
Shikamaru...

160
00:17:30,122 --> 00:17:32,818
We need to go over to where
Kakashi Sensei is right now!

161
00:17:33,859 --> 00:17:35,224
What're you planning to do?

162
00:17:35,761 --> 00:17:36,455
Hey!

163
00:17:38,663 --> 00:17:39,857
I'm going to...

164
00:17:40,866 --> 00:17:41,798
stop this match!

165
00:17:45,237 --> 00:17:48,400
<i>Gaara couldn't possibly be planning</i>
<i>to use that Jutsu!</i>

166
00:18:33,218 --> 00:18:35,812
<i>So he used all the sand for protection...</i>

167
00:18:36,721 --> 00:18:38,621
<i>I didn't think there could be this</i>
<i>much of a difference in the hardness</i>

168
00:18:38,690 --> 00:18:40,681
<i>with a difference in the density</i>
<i>of the sand.</i>

169
00:18:46,631 --> 00:18:48,929
So it's absolute protection.

170
00:18:53,872 --> 00:18:56,568
The sand...
It's covered his entire body.

171
00:18:57,576 --> 00:18:59,840
<i>This is somewhat troublesome.</i>

172
00:19:00,545 --> 00:19:02,843
<i>Now, how will Sasuke proceed?!</i>

173
00:19:06,017 --> 00:19:07,575
Kakashi Sensei!

174
00:19:11,523 --> 00:19:12,387
Naruto!

175
00:19:19,231 --> 00:19:21,495
Huh? What do you want?

176
00:19:22,167 --> 00:19:25,432
Sensei!
Please stop this match right away!

177
00:19:28,373 --> 00:19:32,241
That guy is totally different from us!

178
00:19:32,644 --> 00:19:34,703
He's not normal!

179
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:39,182
Naruto...
What're you saying?

180
00:19:39,818 --> 00:19:42,548
He lives to kill people.

181
00:19:42,787 --> 00:19:43,845
In any case...

182
00:19:44,289 --> 00:19:47,122
If this continues, Sasuke will die!

183
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,718
Jin, Saru,

184
00:19:49,895 --> 00:19:53,831
Ne, Saru, Tori, Tatsuu, Ne, Saru...

185
00:20:05,443 --> 00:20:08,640
<i>There's no mistake about it.</i>
<i>It's that Jutsu!</i>

186
00:20:09,948 --> 00:20:14,385
<i>This isn't good!</i>
<i>Our plan isn't even on Gaara's mind.</i>

187
00:20:15,687 --> 00:20:16,415
Shoot!

188
00:20:17,455 --> 00:20:18,922
Kakashi Sensei!

189
00:21:05,704 --> 00:21:15,773
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

190
00:21:16,214 --> 00:21:27,057
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

191
00:21:37,169 --> 00:21:42,801
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

192
00:21:42,874 --> 00:21:47,834
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

193
00:21:48,213 --> 00:21:53,116
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

194
00:21:53,185 --> 00:21:58,316
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

195
00:21:58,390 --> 00:22:08,561
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

196
00:22:08,867 --> 00:22:19,300
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

197
00:22:19,377 --> 00:22:29,946
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

198
00:22:30,021 --> 00:22:35,584
<i>Forge on strong</i>

199
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:51,337
<i>Sasuke, when I fought you once, I said</i>

200
00:22:51,511 --> 00:22:52,978
<i>Even if one understands visually,</i>

201
00:22:53,045 --> 00:22:54,876
<i>it's meaningless unless one</i>
<i>can move physically.</i>

202
00:22:55,081 --> 00:22:56,810
<i>I was filled with</i>
<i>a sense of superiority.</i>

203
00:22:56,883 --> 00:23:00,375
<i>But now, you have a body that moves</i>
<i>at the same high speed as mine.</i>

204
00:23:00,887 --> 00:23:03,185
<i>Moreover, you have...Sharingan!</i>

205
00:23:03,623 --> 00:23:08,253
Next time,
"Late for the Show, But Ready to Go!
The Ultimate Secret Technique is Born!"

206
00:23:08,661 --> 00:23:11,824
I am really envious of you, Sasuke!
